    gg "You've been here for a week now, right? Seems like you're doing much better."


translate English day7_gr_4b0265fb:


    pl "Not that it's any business of yours."


translate English day7_gr_3e1f1a2e:


    gg "You're right. It's just that Grette likes to stick her nose into other people's problems and has a tendency to ramble. {w}Plus, it's all too easy to get sidetracked, wouldn't you say?"


translate English day7_gr_c7f85dc2:


    gg "I have a feeling I'll be butting into your business in various ways moving forward, though I'm not sure if merely butting in is the right way to put it. Rather..."


