    pl "but I would assume smoking is one of those big no-no's, especially for someone like a bishop. {w}You should be setting a good example for priests like myself, right?"


translate English day7_gr_5de6bdd8:


    gg "You're saying you're inclined to look up to me as an example of exemplary behavior? {w}Hmm... Yes, as you should, of course."


translate English day7_gr_2544d867:


    pl "But you should probably also abstain for the sake of Dr. Grette's health, don't you agree? {w}Especially since she detests people who drink and smoke to excess."


translate English day7_gr_786e3647:


    gg "True..."


translate English day7_gr_00d8f8f0:


    nar "He slowly passes me by, moving out of my way. I hear the familiar sound of the infirmary door opening from somewhere behind me."


translate English day7_gr_e5bd8a62:


    nar "Are those two the only ones currently inside?"


translate English day7_gr_eb1cce37:


    nar "The walls of the infirmary are, in direct contrast to the thin walls that separate the rooms in the dormitory, quite thick, making it almost impossible to hear anything from out in the hall."


translate English day7_gr_abaa25e6:


    nar "But I quicken my steps anyway until I'm running."


translate English day7_gr_5282877a:


    nar "Both large and small objects flit past me. My mind is a chaotic mess as tumultuous, shapeless thoughts suddenly explode into existence."


translate English day7_gr_3e7005d1:


    nar "I have to forget... The angel is the only thing I'm sure of! {w}Don't say a word. Just keep my mouth shut, and my angel will protect me..."


translate English day7_gr_db78e2d4:



    nvl clear
    et "\n Once I get back to the dorms, I find myself staring up at the ceiling, lost in thought. {w}My room is still as bright as if it were the middle of the day despite the lack of candles."


translate English day7_gr_e935db2f:



    nvl clear
    "\n As I stare up at the ceiling, I ruminate on what she told me earlier. I couldn't bring myself to tell her the truth because I was terrified of her hating me."


translate English day7_gr_b386f9c3:


    et "To borrow her expression, all I want is for her to see me as a good kid. {w}She's an adult to me, and I've always wanted adults to see me as such since as far back as I can remember. With that said, she's no longer an adult worthy of my respect."


translate English day7_gr_c3c5d796:



    nvl clear
    "\n Perhaps to someone like her, every sick person is like a child she needs to care for, and her personality is built around caring for them. She seems pretty passionate about it."


translate English day7_gr_85946fcb:


    "\"With hard work and a little bit of faith, nothing is impossible\"... {w}That unfounded hope is the only thing preserving her own psyche."


translate English day7_gr_be74f9cc:


    "Which is why I don't have to worry about her abandoning me. {w}As long as she considers me a patient, she'll never give up on me."


translate English day7_gr_c8b01122:


    "I hesitated before due to my own lack of certainty, but seeing her today solidified that fact in my mind. {w}No matter what, she's my doctor. And as long as I never attain a certain level of maturity in front of her, she always will be."


translate English day7_gr_c1760ba6:


    et "I get into bed in a metaphorical act of turning out the lights. I hope I don't have any dreams tonight."


