    nvl clear


translate English day8_gr_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day8_gr_86045f2c:



    nvl clear
    et "\n Everyone's trying to trick me in some way, but only my angel never lies. {w}No one can punish me. Only the angel has the authority to charge me with a sin. Until then, my soul is innocent."


translate English day8_gr_3092ad51:


    nar "It's morning. I'm not feeling particularly tired, but I curl up under the blankets anyways. {w}I plan on skipping role call like I usually do."


translate English day8_gr_5c6df3a0:


    nar "Nothing happened yesterday, so I feel confident today will go smoothly as well."


translate English day8_gr_934502f6:


    nar "As I ignore the commotion coming from the hall, I can feel the rules I've been struggling to follow since day blur into meaninglessness, one after the other."


translate English day8_gr_171f1bce:


    nar "I was planning on keeping my eyes closed for the rest of the day when I suddenly hear a flurry of knocks on my door."


translate English day8_gr_db790f6e:


    nar "Is it Securett? Without a second thought, I pull the covers back over my head. {w}A few moments later, the sound repeats itself."


translate English day8_gr_2d660025:


    nar "Despite him only being able to bother me on days when he doesn't have much going on, it's still a huge pain in the ass."


translate English day8_gr_36fe8276:


    sc "Finally decided to make an appearance, hrm?"


translate English day8_gr_425ae34e:


    pl "What?"


translate English day8_gr_4ee3420b:


    sc "What do you mean, \"what\"? You're not coming to work today?"


translate English day8_gr_ef59ae98:


    pl "I'm coming..."


translate English day8_gr_0626a9ae:


    sc "Not feeling well?"


translate English day8_gr_d4fbfc7b:


    nar "I..."


