    pl "I don't feel that great. Can you let the bishop know for me?"


translate English day8_gr_6706c249:


    sc "Sigh..."


translate English day8_gr_e45c6b1e:


    nar "What's he sighing for, considering he's the one who told me I didn't have to go?"


translate English day8_gr_ee57dbb4:


    sc "Fine... If you're still feeling bad once it hits noon, pay the infirmary a visit. {w}Better to get whatever is bothering you taken care of before it becomes a problem."


translate English day8_gr_11d637fa:


    pl "Are you serious?"


translate English day8_gr_3e71c505:


    sc "It'll be a huge inconvenience for me as well if you're stuck in that condition forever."


translate English day8_gr_eb1e660c:


    pl "..."


translate English day8_gr_0a258ee8:


    sc "I'll be going then. See you."


translate English day8_gr_decc854e:


    nar "He walks off down the hall without looking back. {w}I'm sure he's well aware I'm not sick by the way I'm acting."


translate English day8_gr_4ac91bcf:


    nar "There's no way anyone could be fooled by such a blatant lie, right? {w}It's just like the other day."


translate English day8_gr_279d5201:


    nar "At the time, I didn't want anything to do with her. Even if it wasn't the right thing to do, it's still her responsibility,"


translate English day8_gr_110704e3:


    nar "and since it wasn't my problem, I shouldn't waste time worrying--even though I ended up being completely correct about."


translate English day8_gr_ad7c601e:


    nar "I'm sure Securett came to a similar realization, which is why he so abruptly ended the conversation without much of a fight."


translate English day8_gr_b3abe96a:


    nar "But what exactly did he mean by my \"condition\"? {w}Was that his way of calling me a lunatic?"


translate English day8_gr_7b8fdf05:


    nar "I just didn't want to go to the office or answer his questions, that's all. I'm sure he's felt the same way at least once, right?"


translate English day8_gr_eb1e660c_1:


    pl "..."


translate English day8_gr_5ab6b1c7:


    nar "The Cleanup Department should have been quiet at this time of day, but it's filled with the chatter of voices. As soon as I step inside, everyone immediately stops talking and turns to face me."


translate English day8_gr_ef6269a1:


    nar "I walk briskly through the room while doing my best to completely ignore them."


translate English day8_gr_4ab5c232:


    nar "I suddenly hear the sound of laughter. As usual, the work order left for me has only a few simple instructions."


translate English day8_gr_97c35ad8:


    nar "I reach into my dusty locker and pull out a heavy tool. There's dried mud caked on the blade."


translate English day8_gr_c48e2603:


    nar "I forgot to clean it off before I put it away."


translate English day8_gr_40ba9d52:


    ex1 "Wow, must be nice, huh? I wish the Magic Department recruited me so I could slack off and not do any real work."


translate English day8_gr_f01b93a5:


    ex2 "Well, you don't have a girlfriend in the Magic Department, so why aren't you working?"


translate English day8_gr_16af4ab6:


    ex1 "He's still a part of the Disposal Squad, isn't he?"


translate English day8_gr_1e9abec1:


    ex2 "And? That guy's clearly not playing with a full deck of cards!"


translate English day8_gr_6073c6cf:


    nar "They cackle as they slap each other on the shoulders and backs. A shiver runs down my spine, not out of irritation but fear."


translate English day8_gr_e4ec4a21:


    nar "The sun is still up, but it's the same haunting chill I remember feeling the first time I came here."


translate English day8_gr_a2b0ad86:


    nar "I try to put my belongings in my bag, but my hands are shaking so badly that I end up dropping my rubber gloves."


translate English day8_gr_cb88bb2a:


    nar "I bend over as I reach out to pick them up, which is exactly when someone's foot stomps down on them."


translate English day8_gr_9408f41e:


    nar "The hem of this mystery man's pants briefly brush against my outstretched fingers."


translate English day8_gr_7f1b68f1:


    ex1 "I'll make sure you find out what happens to guys like you."


