translate English day8_gr_b2bb6f31:



    nvl clear
    "\n My vision fades in and out, like a flashing light. One moment, I'm holding the shovel over my head. {w}The next, I'm holding a chair."


translate English day8_gr_cfbf73a8:


    "Chairs and desks, typically items bound to the ground, fly past my eyes, and I hear the sound of breaking glass. {w}The next thing I know, I'm grabbing a blood-covered man by his collar."


translate English day8_gr_8b6daced:


    "The man I flung aside opens his swollen lips to spit a curse at me. He's about as tall as me, and I'm not all that strong. {w}I guess he's always been weaker than me."


translate English day8_gr_eda3bd1c:


    "As I watch bubbles of drool float behind him through the air, my vision suddenly goes dark. I feel something hit the back of my head."


translate English day8_gr_5f855f82:


    et "I close my eyes against the pain that rips through me. {w}And from within the darkness, I hear the sound of something falling."


translate English day8_gr_8962d49a:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Fucking hell! You son of a bitch! Fucking piece of SHIT!!!\""


translate English day8_gr_4c2d3a23:


    "My rage grows with each word. If I were to take in his hatred and wrath, I know it would have the oddly soothing effect of calming me down. {w}Despite the fact that I feel the same way he does."


translate English day8_gr_805b3208:


    "The cold breeze soothes my skin, and yet my forehead feels like it's burning up, blood oozing from a gash running across it."


translate English day8_gr_fc557e52:


    "\"HA HA HA!!!\""


translate English day8_gr_49854a95:


    et "That crazed laugh is coming from my own throat."


translate English day8_gr_f36b902c:



    nvl clear
    "\n A sudden burst of wind sends sheets of freezing rain flying in through the broken window, but it doesn't bother me."


translate English day8_gr_9cdd2cbf:


    "My throat and skin are burning hot and motes of dust float in my pure-red vision as if they're alive."


translate English day8_gr_39fbcead:


    "A misshapen desk flies past my head and crashes onto the floor in the shadows with a loud bang."


translate English day8_gr_1deb386d:


    et "The emaciated branches swaying violently outside the window look like the blackened fingers of corpses, moving erratically in an almost beckoning gesture."


translate English day8_gr_6606a832:



    nvl clear
    "\n This is like some unending nightmare. But now that I'm finally aware of the pain, I can feel my blood pulsing hotly underneath my cool skin."


translate English day8_gr_b3cf0378:


    et "This isn't a dream at all. I've long since awakened from that painfully long nightmare. {w}I'm no longer trapped within it. I've reached heaven."


translate English day8_gr_7d2ba8fe:


    pl "You think that's funny? Having so much fun living your playboy lifestyle in the temple that you're about to piss yourself in the dark?"


translate English day8_gr_606dd1c3:


    pl "You know what, though? Hey! I didn't say you could talk, asshole. Is your whole thing babbling on endlessly until you make yourself blue in the face?"


translate English day8_gr_62e11cb4:


    pl "You're the type of guy whose lips would be the only thing left if he got tossed into a pool of water, huh?"


translate English day8_gr_36dc0963:


    pl "You'd keep talking even if your tongue was cut out, and yet I have a feeling even you'd finally shut up with a blade buried in your neck, hrm? {w}What do you think, you piece of shit?!"


