    nar "I'd feel a lot better if he'd acted like I was some kind of idiot and I could write off what happened as a mistake from my sleep-addled mind."


translate English day10_gr_f1110302:


    nar "But he basically admitted to it without saying so."


translate English day10_gr_97ecf20d:


    nar "Still... no matter how many times I think about it, I can't shake my doubt. Could it have been someone else?"


