    nar "Pretty much everyone in the Cleanup Department hates my guts after the incident the other day, so it's not out of the question."


translate English day10_gr_8fd304db:


    nar "I find myself cringing at the thought of someone actually being inside my room. {w}I need some kind of weapon to protect myself. Something I can get right now."


