    nar "Blades and guns are confiscated as a general rule upon entering the temple in order to prevent suicide attempts, but it's not strictly enforced."


translate English day10_gr_3de2df3c:


    nar "Maybe I can find something useful in my locker."


translate English day10_gr_400f8f12:


    nar "Even something like a folding saw would be better than nothing at all."


translate English day10_gr_a07f1768:


    pl "...?!" with sshake


