    nar "Surprised, I yank my hand back only to see blood pouring out from between my fingers. {w}I reach for the handle once more as I cautiously try to figure out what hurt me."


translate English day10_gr_aab1e6d2:


    nar "I immediately find a couple spiky thumbtacks haphazardly attached with hardened glue. {w}A malicious prank."


translate English day10_gr_bed64902:


    nar "If this is the state of the door, then there's definitely something worse inside the locker itself."


translate English day10_gr_3ee6f4ab:


    nar "After mentally preparing myself, I open the door and immediately throw myself to the side. {w}I hear the sound of something falling to the floor."


translate English day10_gr_16dc151c:


    nar "I'd instinctively dodged before it smashed into my head, though I have no idea what had been planted inside."


translate English day10_gr_a9178594:


    pl "...!" with sshake


translate English day10_gr_daf57020:


    nar "I cry out in surprise. {w}I would have screamed louder, but I'm in too much shock to make much noise. {w}It's an arm."


translate English day10_gr_8946844d:


    nar "Charred flesh barely hangs onto the pale, emaciated arm, bones sticking out here and there. It's still attached to a woman's corpse."


translate English day10_gr_154148b8:


    nar "Her messy hair hangs down over her face like dry strands of straw. I can see glimpses of her hollowed out cheeks through the rat's nest."


translate English day10_gr_1f99016f:


    nar "Her head is bent at an angle, causing her protruding eyeballs to stare up blankly at the sky. I back away and step into a sticky pool of blood."


translate English day10_gr_8ae257c2:


    nar "The fluid still retained in her body continuously leaks out through the many holes that riddle her skin."


translate English day10_gr_7d5da516:


    nar "I find myself on the verge of collapsing, but I force myself to hold it together. {w}My head feels heavy, but as soon as I lower it, the overwhelming stench of sewage stabs up through my nose."


