    nar "It would be easy enough for someone in the Cleanup Department whose entire job is to transport and take care of corpses to borrow one without anyone noticing, and yet..."


translate English day10_gr_0b6fd820:


    nar "...why would anyone do something like this?"


translate English day10_gr_69ed9c12:


    sc "[na2]?"


translate English day10_gr_11a0a108:


    pl "Uh..."


translate English day10_gr_7f32f1c4:


    sc "...?"


translate English day10_gr_32e384dd:


    nar "I still can't seem to speak."


