    nar "Rotten blood oozes from the crushed flesh. {w}I can hear several priests chattering excitedly about the situation from behind me."


translate English day10_gr_9a9db627:


    pl "For fuck's sake! What are you looking at?!" with sshake


translate English day10_gr_c3ee0e62:


    nar "I shout at them as I begin hyperventilating. The commotion immediately vanishes before returning to its former roar, growing louder by the second."


