    nar "From within the chaos, I clearly hear laughter and insults. {w}I seek out their faces through a film of bright red rage. Who in the world did this?"


translate English day10_gr_e5f6ecaf:


    sc "[na]!" with sshake


translate English day10_gr_eb1e660c_2:


    pl "..."


