    sc "Look... I know you're not in the best of moods, but you're taking this way too far."


translate English day10_gr_69337169:


    pl "Have you lost your damn mind?"


translate English day10_gr_a8bf22ec:


    sc "I'll clean this up, okay? Just please... calm down and think about this. {w}The way I see it, in the state you are now..."


translate English day10_gr_4bc1a665:


    pl "Ugh...!"


translate English day10_gr_126557c4:


    sc "...!!"


translate English day10_gr_4a559d73:


    nar "I vomit, unable to hold it back any longer. {w}The splatters of brown puke mix with the reddish-black blood to form a chaotic blend of colors."


translate English day10_gr_2163980f:


    nar "I hear scattered screams from somewhere behind me. With the world spinning around me, someone manages to catch me before I can fall, and someone else puts an arm around my shoulder."


translate English day10_gr_e0969313:


    nar "My ears are stuffed full of a cacophony of sounds. {w}With the mystery person's help, I'm able to walk, one shaky step after another..."


translate English day10_gr_669bb0bf:


    nar "..."


