    hk "Don't worry. Take as much time as you need to calm down..."


translate English day10_gr_17373561:


    pl "Why was everyone here so early?"


translate English day10_gr_611f9af8:


    hk "I'm sorry?"


translate English day10_gr_71ef58ac:


    hk "Heh... Hee hee hee! You really are amusing, Brother."


translate English day10_gr_eb1e660c_3:


    pl "..."


