    pl "Are you planning on keeping all of this a secret from the Magic Department? This is about getting me to keep my mouth shut, right?"


translate English day10_gr_f7eedd53:


    pl "I know what's going on. The position you're in means you can't hide things from them, huh?"


translate English day10_gr_dc22c049:


    pl "So you act concerned, try to get along with everyone, and pretend like you don't see the bullying I'm dealing with from the other priests since you can't punish me yourself!"


translate English day10_gr_d99fe25a:


    hk "Have you been taking your medicine, Brother?"


translate English day10_gr_5dfd4a93:


    nar "Medicine...?"


translate English day10_gr_04db43ec:


    pl "What does that have to do with anything? Just answer the damn question!"


translate English day10_gr_96e9f14c:


    hk "Hmm... Well, Brother, you are right that my position requires me to maintain friendly relations with the Magic Department even in light of disagreeable behavior,"


translate English day10_gr_e0d22306:


    hk "but are you implying that I hate you because you see yourself as the Magic Department's golden child?"


translate English day10_gr_36f3a7c0:


    nar "Anxious, I reach into my pocket and immediately find the saw I stashed away earlier. Luckily, no one seems to have taken it from me."


translate English day10_gr_436f4f76:


    hk "Heh heh... Hahahaha! {w}You always make me laugh, Brother." with sshake


translate English day10_gr_693a6227:


    hk "Negligent work practices, violent behavior, problems with interpersonal relationships... Is it really a bishop's job to deal with these so-called providences?"


translate English day10_gr_fa41a2c4:


    hk "Enough that Erzsebet would warn someone as lowly as myself?"


translate English day10_gr_a2fd6e59:


    hk "My lord... You poor, unfortunate soul, Brother. It's a shame that your righteousness crumbles in the face of God himself."


translate English day10_gr_29db4a8b:


    pl "Whuh? YOU'RE the one always going on and on about how your ONLY job is to care for your priests!"


translate English day10_gr_78dfb175:


    hk "Yes, of course. As the face of my department, I must watch over the priests placed in my care."


