    hk "But the priests exist for the people who live outside the temple grounds. {w}They do not bully those weaker than them, they do not waver in their faith, and they do not commit immoral acts."


translate English day10_gr_7e2fc8bd:


    hk "They act rationally, no matter what. Anyone unable to follow those four basic principles does not have what it takes to protect another human being."


translate English day10_gr_64ed647b:


    hk "Meaning, according to the providence, my role as bishop is to watch over my flock without interfering with their work."


