    pl "You killed her! Her blood is on your hands! {w}And my life's ruined because of it..."


translate English day10_gr_4f616a40:


    pl "If she were still alive, if you hadn't gone and killed her for your own selfish reasons..."


translate English day10_gr_0822977b:


    hk "Is this a confession, Brother?"


translate English day10_gr_7ddbfafc:


    pl "N-No! I have no sins to confess! I'm asking about the sins YOU committed!" with sshake


translate English day10_gr_14369672:


    hk "Aha! Well that's easy enough. {w}She failed to uphold one of the temple's most basic rules."


translate English day10_gr_614737a5:


    hk "People like her are culled from the flock all the time. {w}Sadly, she was unable to feel remorse for her actions."


translate English day10_gr_3f7f8c8f:


    hk "She was simply unable to make amends, even after giving her one final chance to do so..."


translate English day10_gr_989670f3:


    pl "..."


translate English day10_gr_ad0bdcd5:


    nar "I get ready to stand up."


translate English day10_gr_f0dd4c3c:


    nar "She called me to meet with her in private,"


translate English day10_gr_1b6d3c1b:


    nar "and if all these questions simply lead to being given some vague last chance, then the reason I'm sitting here right now is because..."


translate English day10_gr_e507ed49:


    hk "Have I answered your questions sufficiently?"


translate English day10_gr_eb1e660c_4:


    pl "..."


translate English day10_gr_979b4dc6:


    hk "It's not that I'm not punishing you, but more like I can't. {w}By the way, Brother, how's your soul doing?"


translate English day10_gr_ea9a4c87:


    hk "That's actually the reason why I called you here today... Are you ready to repent for your sins, Brother?"


translate English day10_gr_67aacd2a:


    nar "Not wanting to hear another word, I raise the saw above my head. Everything she has to say is bullshit."


translate English day10_gr_b261ee8c:


    nar "A part of me is afraid that if I keep listening, I'll only end up getting sucked into her crazy philosophy and lose whatever sanity I have left."


translate English day10_gr_58069487:


    nar "Unlike my chair, which crashed to the floor with shrill clatter when I stood up before rolling away, hers remains steadfastly in its original spot."


translate English day10_gr_3c43a3da:


    nar "My palms are slippery with sweat from being clenched in fists inside my pockets this whole time."


translate English day10_gr_e13241af:


    pl "How can you claim an opportunity is fair when you force people into these kinds of situations? {w}This is all your fault!"


translate English day10_gr_9ad0dd66:


    pl "If you want to take responsibility that badly, then die and get out of my way!"


translate English day10_gr_585f3e61:


    hk "That weapon... It means a lot to you, doesn't it?"


translate English day10_gr_04597b0e:


    hk "I stopped them from taking it from you because I know how much you cherish it. {w}And no matter what happens, I do truly believe taking an opportunity from someone is always wrong."


translate English day10_gr_eb1e660c_5:


    pl "..."


translate English day10_gr_afbe1ded:


    hk "I wondered what you might do with that, but now I see. You're going to stab me, yes? {w}If the act of doing so leaves you fulfilled in some way, then as providence decrees..."


translate English day10_gr_65d1a875:


    hk "I'm more than happy for you to do so. {w}Do you understand, Brother?"


translate English day10_gr_979cb37f:


    hk "If you hold an opportunity in your hand, then it is your right to make ample use of it."


translate English day10_gr_20bf5cd5:


    hk "As your bishop, it is my responsibility to gladly accept whichever decision you make."


translate English day10_gr_d0ffafce:


    nar "If I decide to murder her right now, then she can punish me for the mistake I made."


translate English day10_gr_2200254f:


    nar "Sin is physical evidence necessary to punish someone, which is honestly nothing more than a convenient excuse. I never had a chance."


translate English day10_gr_350ab96b:


    nar "Her claim of my being given a chance at all was bullshit right from the start."


translate English day10_gr_3a3944bb:


    nar "I hear a pounding on the door behind me that matches the wild beating of my own heart."


translate English day10_gr_97f59b2a:


    nar "It's the same annoying sound from this morning. Her serene gaze almost seems to whisper to me."


translate English day10_gr_7dc78633:


    nar "Telling me to confess my sins and find peace."


translate English day10_gr_7e69f677:


    nar "I avert my gaze, instead looking down at the blade in my hands. It's nothing more than a dirty folding saw. {w}It's not an opportunity, much less a symbol for sin."


translate English day10_gr_1c1ce8c2:


    nar "To give something as mundane as this meaning of that magnitude is akin to lunacy."


translate English day10_gr_d236730f:


    nar "Which is why I tighten my grip on the handle and run from the room."


translate English day10_gr_38dba98a:


    nar "I feel the back of my head get hot. I run, knowing I have to get as far from her as possible."


translate English day10_gr_5685bb25:


    nar "Laughter follows me down the hall, coming from a woman who I no longer know."


translate English day10_gr_5b7d24cd:


    nar "It clashes with the sound of my teeth grinding together, my eyes hidden from view."


translate English day10_gr_43ed93c7:


    my2 "What are you running from, [na2]?"


translate English day10_gr_eb1e660c_6:


    pl "..."


translate English day10_gr_107884c5:


    my2 "You don't have to look back if you're scared. I can talk to you if it'll help."


translate English day10_gr_eb1e660c_7:


    pl "..."


