    cr "Hey, Dr. Grette? I was wondering... Is it possible for one to be aware of their own mental illness?"


translate English day10_gr_a0a3cfd7:


    gr "That's tough. It depends on the individual. {w}Dealing with a mental illness is hard because it doesn't tend to manifest itself in the same way a physical ailment does..."


