    gr "However... There are plenty of people out there who refuse treatment, just like you said."


translate English day10_gr_ee4240ed:


    gr "Which is its own problem..."


translate English day10_gr_e6bbb4eb:


    gr "It's possible to notice recurring symptoms and use them to diagnose yourself..."


